https://hub.docker.com/r/linagora/james-jpa-sample/tags?page=1&ordering=last_updated
docker run -p "25:25" -p "143:143" linagora/james-jpa-sample:latest

domain : james.local
user01@james.local
password: 1234
this James server will respond to IMAP port 143 and SMTP port 25


